Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_report...max_path_limit(25.10)    timing_report...max_path_limit(25.10)

Name
       timing_report_begin_end_pair_max_path_limit

Syntax
       timing_report_begin_end_pair_max_path_limit <integer>

       Default: 2000000

       Sets  a  limit on the maximum number of paths that can be reported when
       the report_timing -begin_end_pair parameter is specified.

       Note: Higher maximum paths limit may lead to high memory usage and run-
       time.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

